snippet.description:
💿 Get this compilation on Vinyl
↪︎ https://fanlink.to/2amstudysession

After the successful launch of the Study Session vinyl compilation series in December 2019, we are proud to present to you the next one: 2AM. Study Session! Like the first release, this one features 25 carefully selected beats from various talented artists around the world. With beautiful study girl artwork and pink colored vinyl, this is aimed to heighten your focus, calm your nerves, and help you chill 😇

🎨 Download the illustration/animation (& support the artist)
→ https://www.patreon.com/margauxpeltat/

🎵 Tracklist
[00:00] Intro
[00:12] hoogway - Missing Earth
[03:08] cocabona - You
[05:54] Aylior x eaup - Ships
[07:22] spencer hunt x WYS - VHS
[09:02] Dr. Dundiff x allem iversom - Pale Moon
[12:31] E I S U - Puddles
[14:12] lilac - Honey & Lemon
[15:58] WYS - Nautilus
[18:45] steezy prime  x spencer hunt - Compassion 
[20:58] ocha - It's Going to Be a Good Day

[50:03] nothingtosay - Inspect

[59:24] j'san x Epektase - Ghost in my Mind
